NewEraCap.com

node.text: Deuce makes me incredibly proud! Our one-on-one time means the world to me and I know moments like this will impact him, the same way family time impacted me. To all the dads out there, @MetroByTMobile and I see you ruling your day to show your kids to follow their dreams. Happy #FathersDay. #RuleYourDay #Ad 📖: @ladygracebyers
